creator: yoozoo GmbH
descriptionHtml:
The Piranha App is designed to help car dealers to shoot perfect photos of their cars within minutes - in order to speed up their turnover times.

The App will make sure that all cars are photographed exactly the same way so that the car dealer's websites look professional and consistent.

Furthermore Piranha can automatically transfer the photos to a clipping and background replacement service.
descriptionShort: Perfect car photos within no time

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Dear Piranha-Users, our next update is ready for download!
You can expect the following changes:
- implementation of our new NextGen 360° Spin for Android
- addition of a search function in the archive
- optimization of the To-Do-List search function
- small interface adjustments
- further improvements of performance and stability

Have fun photographing,
The Octopus.tools team

title: Piranha automotive photography

creator: yoozoo GmbH
descriptionHtml: With the Piranha app, we offer commercial car dealers an intuitive solution for automotive photography. In addition to creating professional and consistent images according to manufacturer specifications, you will also be able to take 360° exterior shots and interior panoramas using a 360° camera. We can provide manual image cropping as well as cropping using our artificial intelligence. We can deliver the results directly to your DMS and they will also available for download in your Piranha web access. Last but not least, you can also create videos with predefined setup and guides. Use the Piranha app to showcase your vehicles perfectly and boost your sales.
descriptionShort: Perfect car photos within no time
